pageContext.claim: “Did you see the other day where drug dealers got caught at the top, they couldn't get over? We had to get the fire department to get them down. They couldn't get over and they're like mountain climbers. They got used to climbing they got caught because you know that panel? That's an anti-climb panel.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump appears to have made this up. There's no evidence that the migrants who were crossing the wall were carrying drugs. Customs and Border Protection makes no mention of drugs in its news release about the incident.
